    "name": "VAMPIRE SANDWICH",
    "steam_appid": 3014370,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014370/extras/7c9bcc08255e7f1f924710f0933e4cae.poster.avif?t=1766465388\" width=600 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014370/extras/7c9bcc08255e7f1f924710f0933e4cae.webm?t=1766465388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014370/extras/7c9bcc08255e7f1f924710f0933e4cae.mp4?t=1766465388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>VAMPIRE SANDWICH</strong> is a roguelike deckbuilder,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >where you craft and stack sandwiches to serve vampire girls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UNIQUE SANDWICH-BUILDING MECHANICS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stack, stack, stack over 100 unique ingredient cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover your own creative sandwich synergy and combos!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014370/extras/08b0c13d58c3018389660864c058955e.avif?t=1766465388\" width=1024 height=322 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BEAUTIFUL ORIGINAL SOUNDTRACKS (by Meary)</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the cozy kitchen to the tense encounters with hungry vampires,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The beautiful melodies enhance your journey through this dark yet charming world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPERIENCE THE WORLD OF VAMPIRES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience stories with characters that change every day. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hungry vampires may attack you for blood if you don't meet them for too long!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014370/extras/1cf63eb99912c42000aa0332e605a519.poster.avif?t=1766465388\" width=600 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014370/extras/1cf63eb99912c42000aa0332e605a519.webm?t=1766465388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014370/extras/1cf63eb99912c42000aa0332e605a519.mp4?t=1766465388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>VISUAL NOVEL-STYLE ROGUELIKE DECKBUILDER EXPERIENCE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn rewards for fun dates with vampire beauties and maids. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll get better rewards for making choices that please your characters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014370/extras/f651a1395eb6012d11f67c759d90cb83.poster.avif?t=1766465388\" width=600 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014370/extras/f651a1395eb6012d11f67c759d90cb83.webm?t=1766465388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014370/extras/f651a1395eb6012d11f67c759d90cb83.mp4?t=1766465388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >    <strong>BEWARE THEIR THIRST</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vampires don't settle for tasteless sandwiches!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep making delicious sandwiches, or you're going to run out of blood pretty quickly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014370/extras/7e0001a1b50cd2dc3661653ca10c2b83.poster.avif?t=1766465388\" width=600 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014370/extras/7e0001a1b50cd2dc3661653ca10c2b83.webm?t=1766465388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014370/extras/7e0001a1b50cd2dc3661653ca10c2b83.mp4?t=1766465388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
